#### [MODIFY] [MuslimCompanionApp.kt](file:///D:/AI/Projects With AI/Islamic App/Muslim Companion V1/muslim-companion/app/src/main/java/com/example/MuslimCompanionApp.kt)
or
#### [MODIFY] [MainActivity.kt](file:///D:/AI/Projects With AI/Islamic App/Muslim Companion V1/muslim-companion/app/src/main/java/com/example/MainActivity.kt)

Trigger `QuranAssetLoader.seedDatabase()` in a coroutine on app start if not
already seeded. This runs **once** on first install (or DB wipe). Subsequent
launches find the table populated and skip it.

```kotlin
// In Application.onCreate() or MainActivity.onCreate()
lifecycleScope.launch(Dispatchers.IO) {
    if (!quranAssetLoader.isSeeded()) {
        quranAssetLoader.seedDatabase()
    }
}
```

